"  / for commands                                   ! for shell commands         "
"  ctrl + j for newline                             tab to queue message         "
"  @ for file paths                                 ctrl + v to paste images     "
"  ctrl + g to edit in external editor              esc esc to edit previous mess"
"  ctrl + r search history                          ctrl + x then ctrl + u undo l"
"  ctrl + x then 1-9 to switch agent threads        ctrl + o copy markdown       "
"  ctrl + x then ctrl + y copy plain text           ctrl + c to exit             "
"  shift + tab to change mode                                                    "
"  ctrl + t to view transcript                                                   "
